---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Auctions">
    <div class="about-container">
        <h1>About Auctions</h1>
        <p>
            Auctions are a dynamic and exciting way to buy and sell items, ranging from real estate and vehicles to collectibles and antiques. They bring together buyers and sellers in a competitive environment, ensuring fair market value through bidding.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our platform is designed to provide you with the latest auction listings, detailed information, and tools to participate with confidence. Whether you're a seasoned bidder or new to auctions, we aim to make the process seamless and enjoyable.
        </p>
        <p>
            Explore the world of auctions and discover unique opportunities to acquire valuable items. Stay informed, bid smart, and enjoy the thrill of winning at auction.
        </p>
    </div>

    <style>
        .about-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</Layout>